The '''Adebsu Clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. Based on the [[Betu/Legends|Betu]] continent, it owned the small [[Adebsu Enclave]]. It owed its loyalties to the [[Chekkoo clan/Legends|Chekkoo clan]].

